> Oh, you must be using an old version of Bazel? `liblibtensorflow.so.ifso` is the import library you want.

I tried to rename the `liblibtensorflow.so.ifso` to ` libtensorflow.so.if.lib` and import it in Visual Studio, but this error still occurred.
